            <section>
                <h1><a href="#">Adzap</a></h1>
                <p class="lead"><a href="index.html">Get mad for ads</a></p>
                <hr>
                <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span> Posted on Aug 30 at 1:30 PM</p>
                <hr>
                <img src="images/adzap.JPG" class="img-responsive">
                <hr>
                <p>In addition to technical knowledge one also needs the art to present their ideas in an
appealing way, hence Adzap. It's a variation of the popular business plan presentations
which aims at developing market knowledge and skills among the participants and at
the same time test.
Their creativity and presentation prowess enabling them to know and learn the creative
area of the industry.</p>
                <hr>
            </section>


             <section>
                <h1><a href="#">Crossfire</a></h1>
                <p class="lead"><a href="index.html">The Debate Competition</a></p>
                <hr>
                <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span> Posted on Aug 31 at 11:00 AM</p>
                <hr>
                <img src="images/co2.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <hr>
                <p>The debate is an integral part of Expressions'17. As one needs to have the wherewithal
to present their views and ideas compellingly, Crossfire aims at improving the
communication skills of the participants as well as bolsters their confidence and
enhances their personality.</p>


            <section>
                <h1><a href="#">The Big Fight</a></h1>
                <p class="lead"><a href="index.html">The Group Dicussion</a></p>
