                <hr>
                <p>Group Discussion, the most quintessential element that goes into the making of a
complete individual. It aims at improving group behaviour and individual dynamics
simultaneously.</p>
                
                <hr>
            </section>

             <section>
                <h1><a href="#">Critic</a></h1>
