            </section>

            <section>
                <h1><a href="#">Imagram</a></h1>
                <p class="lead"><a href="index.html">Into your brain</a></p>
                <hr>
                <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span> Posted on Aug 31 at 11:00 AM</p>
                <hr>
                <img src="images/xyz1.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <hr>
                <p>Imagram is a picture perception testimonial event. The participants are asked questions
based on the sequence of images.</p>
                
                <hr>
            </section>
            
            <section>
                <h1><a href="#">Senate</a></h1>
                <p class="lead"><a href="index.html"> Youth </a></p>
                <hr>
                <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span> Posted on Aug 31 at 11:00 AM</p>
                <hr>
                <img src="images/blog1.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <hr>
                <p>It's a parliamentary debate in which two teams (opposition and ruling party) discuss an
agenda and formulate policy. Agendas are given to them at the spot and a limited
number of time is given to think and make notes about the given topic.</p>
                
                <hr>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h1><a href="#">Street Battle</a></h1>
                <p class="lead"><a href="index.html">A dance face-off</a></p>
                <hr>
                <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span> Posted on Aug 30 at 11:00 AM</p>
                <hr>
                <img src="images/blog2.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <hr>
                <p>This is a dance face-off event that takes place between crowds. For all the dancing feet, this event is all one can ask for.</p>
                
